						               													<description>With the collapse of the Tower of Imprisoned Demons, the thousands of demons once again rampaged the earth. To avoid being overwhelmed by the creatures, the Great God Nuwa used the magic of returning to the soul to create the Xiaoyao Illusion that temporarily trapping dangerous demons in it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The celestial heroes of all time and space have received the message from Nuwa: Please come to the Illusion to conquer the demons and save the common people! The number of powerhouses with the highest merits will get my reward-go back in time and change the thing that makes you most regrettable. Therefore, the powerhouses from all walks of life have packed their bags and set off for the Xiaoyao Illusion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The players are divided into two teams, A and B, according to the number of players in the game. Each player plays a different hero with special skills. Players take their turns one by one. A turn includes several phases, during which you can trigger event cards, play scrolls, and get equipped. The most important phase is the Battle Phase, during which you can trigger a battle with monsters. Your teammates can support you and your opponents can interfere. Cards and skills can be used to influence the battle. If you win, you get the winning effect and may keep the monster as your pet, otherwise, you have to get punished for losing.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the monster deck is empty, the team with higher points from pets wins! You can also win by killing all your opponents. Don't forget the love stories from the main video game because the heroes won't hesitate to sacrifice their lives to save their lovers!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
